```

**5G Code Implementation:**
- **Physical Unclonable Functions (PUFs)**: 1,024-bit silicon fingerprint
- **Post-Quantum Cryptography**: CRYSTALS-Kyber + Dilithium
- **Homomorphic Encryption**: Data processed while encrypted
- **Blockchain Anchoring**: Daily hashes to Ethereum/Bitcoin
- **Zero-Knowledge Proofs**: Access verification without data exposure

**Safeway Guardian Features:**
1. **Geofencing**: Data accessibility based on GPS/5G triangulation
2. **Temporal Access**: Time-based encryption (Shamir's secret sharing)
3. **Multi-Persona**: Single drive presents different data to different users
4. **Forensic Logging**: Immutable audit trail in silica storage
```

3. MANUFACTURING PROCESS FLOW

Phase 1: Core Fabrication (Cleanroom Class 10)

```
Week 1-2: Silica Storage Medium
1. SiO₂ vapor deposition on 300mm wafer
2. Femtosecond laser patterning (10^17 voxels/wafer)
3. Atomic force microscopy verification
4. Dicing into 25mm x 25mm storage cores

Week 3-4: AI SoC Assembly
1. TSMC 3nm process for main die
2. Heterogeneous integration (chiplet design)
3. Through-silicon vias (TSVs) for vertical stacking
4. Underfill and encapsulation
```

Phase 2: Protective Structure Assembly

```
Week 5-6: Composite Shield Growth
1. Atomic layer deposition of DLC coating
2. Microfluidics injection of shear-thickening layer
3. Powder bed fusion 3D printing of titanium lattice
4. Sputtering deposition of mu-metal layer

Week 7-8: Final Integration
1. Robotic pick-and-place of all components
2. Laser welding in argon atmosphere
3. Vacuum backfilling with inert gas
4. Hermetic sealing via glass frit bonding
```

Phase 3: Testing & Calibration

```
Week 9-10: Qualification Testing
• Thermal cycling: -55°C to 125°C, 1,000 cycles
• Vibration: 20G RMS, 10Hz-2kHz
• Shock: 1,500G, 0.5ms half-sine
• Radiation: 100kRad total ionizing dose
• Salt fog: 96 hours at 35°C

Week 11-12: Data Integrity Verification
• Full surface scan: 100% of voxels verified
• Error rate testing: <10^-18 unrecoverable bit error rate
• Security validation: NIST FIPS 140-3 Level 4
• Performance benchmarking
```

